  	- Pin Assignment must be set to GPIO function 
  	  (15.6.5.1 Dual-Function Pin Assignment Registers)
     - Output Data Register must be set/reset 
       (15.6.1 Port Output Data Registers (PORTn))
  	*/
  	
  	
